Title : Wolfgang Lindenhofer
Text : '''Wolfgang Lindenhofer''' is an [[Austria]]n [[hair stylist]] and [[make-up artist]] living and working in [[Vienna]].

== Career ==
Lindenhofer styled several personalities from [[music]], [[film]] and [[fashion]] while they stayed in Austria − amongst them musicians [[Hercules and Love Affair|Andrew Butler]], [[Feist (singer)|Feist]] and [[Róisín Murphy]],<ref>Katharina Seidler: [http://derstandard.at/1381370304192/Hercules-and-Love-Affair-Modeshooting-mit-Kultmusiker-Andy-Butler Hercules and Love Affair: Modeshooting mit Kultmusiker Andy Butler], ''[[Der Standard]]'', October 31, 2013</ref><ref>Carmen Rüder: [http://diepresse.com/home/leben/mode/621139/Stylisten_Von-Kopf-bis-Fuss-mit-Haut-und-Haar?from=suche.intern.portal Stylisten: Von Kopf bis Fuß, mit Haut und Haar], ''[[Die Presse]]'', Dezember 23, 2010</ref>  [[Burgtheater]] actresses [[Jasna Fritzi Bauer]] und [[Birgit Minichmayr]],<ref>Britta Hammelstein: [http://www.interview.de/kunst/theater-jetzt-britta-hammelstein On Birgit Minichmayr], ''[[Interview (magazine)|Interview]]'', January 16, 2014</ref> [[movie star]]s [[Pamela Anderson]], [[Isabelle Huppert]] and [[Isabella Rossellini]], as well as models [[Naomi Campbell]], [[Milla Jovovich]], [[Carmen Kass]], [[Karolína Kurková]] and many more. He collaborated with photographers such as  [[Andreas Bitesnich]], [[Michel Comte]], [[Thomas Lohr]], [[Elfie Semotan]], [[Mario Testino]] and [[Erwin Wurm]]. His work has been published in nearly every  Austrian paper and magazine,<ref>[http://www.faq-magazine.com/magazine/2010/07/faq-magazine-07.html FAQ], retrieved April 26, 2014</ref><ref>[http://www.michelmayer.at/press/presse/1012_wiener.pdf WIENER], retrieved April 26, 2014</ref><ref>[http://diepresse.com/home/leben/mode/740662/Schaustrecke_Wer-mag-wen Die Presse], retrieved April 26, 2014</ref><ref>[http://kurier.at/lebensart/style/vienna-awards-for-fashion-lifestyle-bar-refaeli-kam-sah-und-siegte/6.282.350 Kurier], retrieved April 26, 2014</ref><ref>[http://www.krone.at/Stars-Society/Model_Refaeli_mit_Papa_bei_den_Vienna_Awards-Schoen._schoener._Bar-Story-355596 Kronenzeitung], retrieved April 26, 2014</ref><ref>[http://www.woman.at/a/vienna-awards-fashion-lifestyle-354174 Woman], retrieved April 26, 2014</ref> as well as in [[AnOther Magazine]] and [[Neon (magazine)|Neon]],<ref>[http://tempomodels.blogspot.co.at/2013/01/kira-julian-for-neon-magazine-by-maria.html kira & julius for neon magazine], retrieved April 26, 2014</ref> in the German edition of [[Interview (magazine)|Interview]], in [[Marie Claire]], [[Sleek (magazine)|Sleek]], [[L'Officiel]] and in the Indian edition of [[Harper’s Bazaar]].

The stylist was employed at several  [[Runway (fashion)|runway shows]] at the [[fashion week]] in [[Paris]], i.e. for [[Fabric Interseason]], [[Wendy & Jim]], [[Cosmic Wonder]] and [[Petar Petrov (fashion)|Petar Petrov]]. In Paris he also assisted [[Tomohiro Ohashi]] at runway shows of [[Maison Martin Margiela]], [[Zuhair Murad]] and [[Maxime Simoëns]]. He was committed to campaigns for national and international brands such as [[Bipa|BIPA]], [[Claudia Brandmair|Brandmair]], [[Braun (company)|Braun]], [[Heinrich Deichmann-Schuhe GmbH|Deichmann]], [[Salvatore Ferragamo]], [[Kniže & Comp.]], [[Levi’s]], [[Mexx]], [[Nokia]], [[Palmers Textil AG|Palmers]], [[Popp & Kretschmer]], [[Seagram|Royal Stag]], [[Roy Robson]], [[Silhouette (eyewear)|Silhouette]], [[Vöslauer]], [[Wüstenrot]], [[X-ray (Mode)|X-ray]]. For several times, he was engaged by Dame [[Vivienne Westwood]]; in December 2013, she designed the costumes for the dancers at the  [[Vienna New Year's Concert]] of the [[Vienna Philharmonic]], Lindenhofer created the hair styling.<ref>[http://derstandard.at/1385171398384/Tanz-das-Jahr---Das-Shooting Tanz das Jahr - Das Shooting], ''[[Der Standard]]'', Dezember 30, 2013</ref> Since 2005, he is responsible for the ''Celebrity Styling'' at the [[Life Ball]] in Vienna. Since 2013, Lindenhofer serves as a teacher at the [[University of Arts and Industrial Design Linz|University of Arts and Industrial Design]] in [[Linz]].

==Film==
* Vogelfrei, Hors la Loi, Outlaw (2011) - Make-Up Artist

==Accolades==
* 2010 [[Vienna Fashion Award]], category ''Hair Stylist''
* 2013 [[Vienna Fashion Award]], category ''Hair Stylist''

